<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PROJETO - PINHAINTERPRISE</title>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Inicio</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Serviços</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Produtos</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contato</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>Bem-Vindo a PINHAINTERPRISE</h1>
            <p>Desbloqueie sua creatividade com nossos serviços de conteudo</p>
            <a href="#" class="cta-button">Inicie aqui</a>
        </section>

        <section class="services">
            <h2>Nossos Serviços</h2>
            <div class="service">
                <img src="service1.jpg" alt="Service 1">
                <h3>Design Customizável</h3>
                <p>Oferecemos um custom-design para produtos de artesanato.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <img src="service2.jpg" alt="Service 2">
                <h3>Action Figures</h3>
                <p>Crie seu próprio action figure personalizado utilizando nossa avançada tecnologia de impressão 3D.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <img src="service3.jpg" alt="Service 3">
                <h3>Estatuetas</h3>
                <p>hmmmm... Está criando um novo Oscar? Chegou a lugar certo.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 PINHAINTERPRISE. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
        }

        nav ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }


        .hero {
            background-image: url('hero.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            background-color: #ff6600;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }


        .services {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }

        .services h2 {
            font-size:
                32px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .services .service {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .services .service img {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .services .service h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .services .service p {
            font-size: 18px;
        }


        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }


        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero {
                padding: 50px;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 32px;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .services {
                padding: 30px;
            }

            .services .service img {
                width: 150px;
                height: 150px;
            }

            .services .service h3 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .services .service p {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</body>

</html>
